The paper discusses the automatic creation of concept maps from textual sources, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method uses statistical and data mining techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of linguistic tools, which can also be related to deep learning (cs.DL) approaches in natural language processing.
